chmod using change file permission

users are users,groups,others
File permissions are read+write+execute

add a permission to users
chmod u+x file

remove a permission for group
chmod g-w file

add read+write permission to others
chmod o+rw file

add a permission to all users
chmod a+rwx file

add a permission to user+group
chmod ug=rwx file

apply a permission to u+g+o
chmod u+rwx,g+rw,o+w file

